The Keiser Report  No. 160			
= Max Keiser and Stacy Herbert =
Thursday, 30 June 2011


[sebaygo1]


This time Max and Stacy report on oil dumps and contango and on organizing counterattacks with silver. 

In the second half of the show, Max talks to Jeff Berwick of DollarVigilante.com about manipulation of oil and silver markets and new currencies and dead ones.
